---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="About">
  <Header slot="header" />

  <section class="about">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    <div class="content">
      <p>I'm a Software Engineer who builds sustainable, efficient tools that make design and construction workflows less of a headache. Since I started out as a BIM Engineer, I've seen plenty of AEC pain points up close, and that pushes me to create better, more thoughtful products.</p>

      <h2>Professional Journey</h2>
      <p>My career has evolved from BIM Coordination to Senior Software Engineering, giving me a unique perspective on both the user needs and technical implementation of AEC solutions.</p>

      <ul class="timeline">
        <li><strong>Automation Developer</strong> – Building tools to solve repetitive tasks and boost productivity</li>
        <li><strong>Software Engineer</strong> – Architecting scalable solutions for complex AEC problems</li>
        <li><strong>Open Source Contributor</strong> – Giving back to the community through libraries and tools</li>
        <li><strong>BIM Coordinator</strong> – Understanding workflows, pain points, and collaboration challenges</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Technical Expertise</h2>
      <div class="skills-grid">
        <div class="skill-category">
          <h3>AEC Software</h3>
          <p>Autodesk Revit, Navisworks, BIM 360, Tekla – deep knowledge of industry-standard tools and APIs</p>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-category">
          <h3>Backend Development</h3>
          <p>C#, Python, Node.js – building scalable services with ASP.NET, FastAPI, and Express.js</p>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-category">
          <h3>Frontend Development</h3>
          <p>React, TypeScript, WPF – creating responsive UIs and desktop applications</p>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-category">
          <h3>DevOps & Infrastructure</h3>
          <p>Azure, AWS, Docker, GitHub Actions, Nuke.Build – automating builds and deployments</p>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-category">
          <h3>Databases</h3>
          <p>PostgreSQL, MySQL – designing and optimizing data models for AEC applications</p>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-category">
          <h3>Testing & Quality</h3>
          <p>Unit Testing, Integration Testing, NUnit, Jest, PyTest – building reliable software</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>What I'm Passionate About</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Problem-Solving</strong> – Tackling complex automation challenges that improve workflows</li>
        <li><strong>Open Source</strong> – Contributing to tools like pyRevit that empower the AEC community</li>
        <li><strong>Learning</strong> – Always picking up new technologies and methodologies</li>
        <li><strong>Quality</strong> – Building sustainable, maintainable code that stands the test of time</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Education & Certifications</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>University of Helsinki</strong> – Fullstack Development (2025-2026)</li>
        <li><strong>42 Coding School</strong> – Computer Science (2025)</li>
        <li><strong>Autodesk Certified Professional</strong> – Revit Architecture & Structure</li>
        <li><strong>Various Online Certifications</strong> – JavaScript, Python, C#, SQL, Data Science</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Languages</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>English</strong> – Fluent</li>
        <li><strong>Spanish</strong> – Working Proficiency</li>
      </ul>

      <p style="margin-top: 2rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
        Interested in collaborating? Check out my projects and posts, or reach out through my social links.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .about h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .content {
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .content p {
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .content h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .content h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .content ul {
    list-style-position: inside;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .content li {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .timeline {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .timeline li {
    margin: 0.75rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline li::before {
    content: '•';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .skills-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .skill-category {
    padding: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    background-color: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .skill-category h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .skill-category p {
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }
</style>
